      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-EB4361C5-157F-4387-9887-3619E01F5DC3" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DBB4647D-1834-4C02-8A6A-55178692ECB1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Based on Putaway Control Indicator and Storage Type Search Sequence</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9D1F64A6-9839-4ABF-AF63-DED6647B2D3E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Based on Storage Section Indicator and Storage Section Search Sequence</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-63996DF8-0DAA-4DEF-934D-AF29B09C985B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Storage Type, Storage Section and Storage Bin information will be entered manually</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2A51D0C5-9EF5-4E8C-ABE4-D33CC5D09951" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Confirmation of Putaway Task and Exceptions during Putaway are captured in this L3.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9F99F473-CC1B-42B2-9E58-CB9E71EBEE79" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>In this task, at  backend, if there are any limitations at Bin Type Level, those will be automatically considered by the system. 
For example, if the Bin has reached its capacity, system will give detailed error message and will not allow to create Putaway Task</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E8B897C6-E289-4866-BB7E-234E4BC4FE6C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Goods Receipt will act as  Putaway Label- Yet to be Finalized</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-AD180718-3F28-4EB3-97F1-B7A1AB6AC900" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/99ed2fb6879346238999fda867d77df1</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Kommand Auto Store</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F51911E3-9213-45E3-9A58-3868349E27A6" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Forecast To Stock
Process Group: L Logistics &amp; Inventory Management
Process Name: L-040-120 Determine Put-away Location</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7FA778FE-AA21-4991-9CDB-483261992543" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>R2 Flow Applicable to : Finished Goods
R3 Flow Applicable to : Non Finished Goods for below Scenario
                                         Stock Transfer Order (STO) : Spares, AT Indirect Materials and Silicon
Production Orders - Silicon</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
